\& #               \*(AqSAFERP\*(Aq, \*(AqSAFER_K128\*(Aq, \*(AqSAFER_K64\*(Aq, \*(AqSAFER_SK128\*(Aq, \*(AqSAFER_SK64\*(Aq,
\& #               \*(AqSEED\*(Aq, \*(AqSkipjack\*(Aq, \*(AqTwofish\*(Aq, \*(AqXTEA\*(Aq, \*(AqIDEA\*(Aq, \*(AqSerpent\*(Aq
